    <div class="our-vision">
      <h1 style="padding: 20px">Our vision</h1>
      <p>
        The rise of e-commerce and online platforms has created new
        opportunities for farmers to reach a broader audience and sell their
        products directly to consumers. However, despite these advancements,
        many farmers still face significant challenges. They often encounter
        middlemen who take a substantial share of their profits, and the
        complexity of reaching consumers directly can be daunting. This gap
        between producers and consumers can lead to both financial and
        logistical hurdles for farmers.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today, we present a solution that not only addresses these challenges
        but also paves the way for a more sustainable and equitable agricultural
        ecosystem. Our platform is designed to empower farmers to sell their
        goods directly to consumers, cutting out the intermediaries, and
        ensuring that both the parties benefit.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our vision is simple yet profound: To create a user-friendly website
        that serves as a bridge between farmers and consumers, fostering a
        direct and transparent relationship. We aim to provide farmers with a
        digital marketplace where they can showcase their products, set their
        prices, and connect with customers who appreciate the value of fresh,
        locally sourced goods. We will explore the many benefits this platform
        offers to both farmers and consumers. From increased income for farmers
        to access to high-quality, farm-fresh produce for consumers, the
        advantages are numerous and promising.
      </p>
